patial resolution after introducing the challenges of the field and reviewing current approaches slac physicist stefan mannsfeld will describe a novel approach for making thin flexible plastic pressure sensors with unprecedented sensitivity and responsiveness he will show how the sensors are fabricated and how they work and the prospect they give for creating an artificial sense of touch attending a lecture maps and directions slac 50th anniversary privacy statement
